	(38888, 'Fantastic Four (1998) #584 (2ND PRINTING VARIANT)', 'jpg', 584, '2.99', '', 'It\'s the return of Galactus, a trip to Nu-World, the Old Kings of Atlantis and Namor, the all-new Yancy Street Gang, and the day the Thing becomes human again. Join Jonathan Hickman and superstar artist Steve Epting in THREE, part 2: \'Congratulations, Mr. Grimm...You\'re Human Again.\'\' Rated A ...$2.99', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/38888'),
