	(13535, 'FANTASTIC FOUR VISIONARIES: WALTER SIMONSON VOL. 1 TPB (Trade Paperback)', 'jpg', 1, '19.99', '', 'After a string of successes with THOR, X-FACTOR and AVENGERS, it\'s sensational Simonson storytelling for Marvel\'s First Family - starting when the FF\'s Congressional hearing is disrupted by dozens of vengence-seeking villains! After the famous foursome - plus Ms. Marvel - deal with the Capitol chaos, a time anomaly sends them to find the future\'s fate! But while Kang and Nebula take up their time, will the universe fall to Galactus? Guest-starring Thor, Iron Man and Death\'s Head! Collecting FANTASTIC FOUR #334-341.\r<br>192 PGS./Rated A  ...$19.99 \r<br>', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/13535'),
