	(22058, 'X-Men Vs. Apocalypse Vol. 2: Ages of Apocalypse (Trade Paperback)', 'jpg', 0, '29.99', 'http://comicstore.marvel.com/X-Men-Vs-Apocalypse-Vol-2-Ages-of-Apocalypse-0/digital-comic/33989?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'The Shi\'Ar on the Moon, Cable and his wife in Egypt, Wolverine in the Negative Zone - what\'s wrong with this picture? Apocalypse has risen from the past to change timelines until he finds one he likes - but when the original X-Man looks him in the eye, both men are lost, leaving the X-Men to comb the world for friend and enemy alike! Will Cyclops literally become the thing he fears and hates the most, and vice versa? And where does the Red Skull fit into all of this? Anywhere he wants to! Guest-starring the Hulk, Machine Man, Deathlok and more! Collecting X-51 #8, UNCANNY X-MEN #378 and ANNUAL 1999, CABLE #77, WOLVERINE #148,\r<br>X-MEN UNLIMITED #26, X-MEN #98 and X-MEN: THE SEARCH OF CYCLOPS #1-4.\r<br>Rated T+ ...$29.99 \r<br>ISBN: 978-0-7851-2264-7\r<br>', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/22058'),
	(17290, 'What If? Annihilation (2007) #1', 'jpg', 1, '2.99', 'http://marvel.com/digitalcomics/view.htm?iid=8743&utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'The wave of ANNIHILATION nearly ravaged the cosmos...but WHAT IF Annihilus was not defeated in the outskirts of our galaxy? WHAT IF he brought his devastating alien armada to Earth? At the height of CIVIL WAR and SILENT WAR, can our planet\'s mightiest heroes put aside their differences long enough to save all of humanity?\r<br>Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/17290'),
	(16209, 'PARADISE X VOL. 2 TPB (Trade Paperback)', 'jpg', 2, '29.99', '', 'The epic, visionary EARTH X saga concludes.  Will the Heroes of Earth be able to solve the problems of the Paradise they helped create? Will their quest for a new Death entity succeed so the pain and suffering of the world\'s population ceases? Collecting PARADISE X #6-12,  RAGNAROK, DEVILS, A, X.\r<br>\r<br>352 PGS./Rated T+ ...$29.99 \r<br>\r<br>ISBN: 0-7851-2416-0 \r<br>\r<br>\r<br>', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/16209'),
	(15902, 'Paradise X Vol. 1 (Trade Paperback)', 'jpg', 0, '9.99', '', 'In EARTH X, Captain America, the Fantastic Four, Thor, the Hulk and the X-Men discovered that their purpose - and the meaning of all super heroes and mutated people in the universe - was nothing more than to protect their host planet, in this case Earth, from outside invasion. They learned super heroes are merely biological antibodies to protect a growing embryo within the Earth. An embryo for the Celestial race: This is the way these Gods fought back - only to cause a terrible ecological imbalance, a rift at its core that in time would wipe out all life on the planet. In UNIVERSE X, Captain Marvel was reborn on Earth years after his death. But he also still claimed to walk in the realm of the unliving, where Earth\'s fallen champions still exist. Mar-Vell led a team of heroes in a quest for the greatest weapons of mass destruction on Earth, suggesting this would limit the destruction caused by the growing power struggle on the planet. But this was not the only reason. For his crusade on Earth only supported and armed a battle he fought in the realm of the fallen, a battle against Death herself. Those living champions who died in his collection of artifacts were added to the battle raging in this other realm. Mar-Vell led a charge against Death and killed her. But now that Death is dead, no one will ever die again. They may writhe in pain in hospitals because their bodies have been broken beyond repair, but they will not die. They will call out for an end to their suffering. They will cry out for peace but there will be no answer. Paradise will be denied them. Yes. Death is truly dead. Long live the living. Collecting PARADISE X #0-5, PARADISE X: XEN and HERALDS #1-3.\r<br>304 PGS./Rated T+ ...$29.99\r<br>ISBN: 0-7851-2415-2\r<br>', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/15902'),
	(5795, 'Annihilation (2006) #6', 'jpg', 6, '2.99', 'http://comicstore.marvel.com/Annihilation-6/digital-comic/5076?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'Nova and Annihilus face off in a fight to the finish with the fates of two, count \'em, two, universes at stake.  You think that\'s bad?  Wait until you see what happens when Galactus decides to go to war.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/5795'),
	(5529, 'Annihilation (2006) #4', 'jpg', 4, '2.99', 'http://comicstore.marvel.com/Annihilation-4/digital-comic/5074?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'Left behind, can Drax survive... Thanos takes action... and Nova sets course on a suicide mission.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/5529'),
	(5230, 'Annihilation (2006) #3', 'jpg', 3, '2.99', 'http://comicstore.marvel.com/Annihilation-3/digital-comic/5073?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'Nova\'s United Front is divided. Nova sets off on a desperate mission. Ronan heads to Hala to free the Kree race. And everyone else is just trying to survive! And what\'s Drax\'s secret agenda, anyway?', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/5230'),
	(4822, 'Annihilation: The Nova Corps (2006) #1', 'jpg', 1, '3.99', '', 'Get caught up on all of the players in the Annihilation event - just in time for this month\'s ANNIHILATION #1! Featuring Annihilus, Nova, Ronan, the Silver Surfer, the Super-Skrull, Thanos and more - all from the Xandarian Worldmind files of the Nova Corps!\r<br>48 PGS NO ADS/Rated A ...$3.99\r<br>', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/4822'),
	(4788, 'Annihilation (2006) #1', 'jpg', 1, '2.99', 'http://comicstore.marvel.com/Annihilation-1/digital-comic/4048?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'One empire has fallen. Two heroes are dead.It all comes together here! Individually, the Silver Surfer, Super-Skrull, Ronan and Nova have faced down the Annihilation Wave... and lost! Now, they must unite those who remain or die by Annihilus\' hand!  The Annihilation has only begun!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/4788'),
	(4473, 'Annihilation: Nova (2006) #4', 'jpg', 4, '2.99', 'http://comicstore.marvel.com/Annihilation-Nova-4/digital-comic/5080?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'Driven to regain his dignity and burdened by the fate of Xandar, Nova faces the Annihilation Wave head on and unleashes the full power of the Nova Force! But is that enough against such a vast force of cosmic destruction? And if it isn\'t, who will stand with him in that last battle? Quasar? Drax?\r<br>Guest starring QUASAR and DRAX THE DESTROYER!\r<br>Interlocking cover with all three other ANNIHILATION covers! \r<br>32 PGS./Rated A ...$2.99\r<br>', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/comics/4473');
INSERT INTO `events` (`eventsId`, `eventsTitle`, `eventsExtension`, `eventsDescription`, `eventsUrl`, `eventsDetail`) VALUES
	(269, 'Secret Invasion', 'jpg', 'The shape-shifting Skrulls have been infiltrating the Earth for years, replacing many of Marvel\'s heroes with impostors, setting the stage for an all-out invasion.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/269', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/269/secret_invasion?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(296, 'Chaos War', 'jpg', 'When the Chaos King embarks on a campaign to wipe out all of existence, Hercules gathers the God Squad to stand in his way! Writers Greg Pak and Fred Van Lente join artist Khoi Pham to pit Herc and his rag tag team√¢‚Ç¨‚Äùincluding Thor, the Silver Surfer and Amadeus Cho√¢‚Ç¨‚Äùagainst an all-powerful evil as dead heroes and villains rise around them!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/296', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/296/chaos_war?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(238, 'Civil War', 'jpg', 'After a horrific tragedy raises questions on whether or not super heroes should register with the government, longtime Avengers teammates Captain America and Iron Man end up on opposite sides of the argument! Writer Mark Millar and artist Steve McNiven split the Marvel Universe in two as friend fights friend in one of the most celebrated and successful events of all-time!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/238', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/238/civil_war?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(302, 'Fear Itself', 'jpg', 'The Serpent, God of Fear and brother to the Allfather Odin, rises to challenge Earth√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s Mightiest in a seven-issue event written by Matt Fraction with art by Stuart Immonen! As the Worthy, heralds of the Serpent, lay waste to the Marvel Universe, how can Thor, Captain America, Iron Man and the Avengers turn back the tide of fear?', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/302', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/302/fear_itself?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(270, 'Secret Wars', 'jpg', 'The most powerful heroes and villains in the Marvel Universe square off on Battleword with the victor promised their greatest dreams and desires! Writer Jim Shooter and artists Mike Zeck and Bob Layton introduce the Beyonder in a 12-issue event featuring the Avengers, the X-Men, the Fantastic Four, Spider-Man, Magneto, Doctor Doom and more!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/270', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/270/secret_wars?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(273, 'Siege', 'jpg', 'When Norman Osborn gathers his evil Cabal to attack Asgard, Captain America leads the Avengers to end the Dark Reign! In a four-issue event written by Brian Michael Bendis with art by Olivier Coipel, Earth\'s Mightiest reunite to oppose their dark counterparts and kick start a Heroic Age!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/273', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/273/siege?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(227, 'Age of Apocalypse', 'jpg', 'In a twisted version of the world they knew, the X-Men battle against the eternal mutant Apocalypse as Bishop seeks to repair the timeline. Legion, Xavier\'s own son, attempts to kill off all of Xavier\'s enemies; however, when Legion attempts to murder Magneto, Xavier sacrifices his own life to save Magnus. As a result, Magneto casts off his anti-human sentiments and carries on Xavier\'s dream of peaceful co-existence, thereby founding the X-Men.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/227', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/227/age_of_apocalypse?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(293, 'Annihilation: Conquest', 'jpg', 'The Phalanx have a new leader in the killer robot Ultron, and he\'s looking for nothing less than univesal conquest! They\'ve already taken the Kree and assimilated heroes like Ronan and Drax; can a rag tag group including Star-Lord, Quasar, Wraith and the reborn Adam Warlock stop them?', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/293', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/293/annihilation_conquest?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(233, 'Atlantis Attacks', 'jpg', 'Ghaur returns to complete his quest to resurrect the evil god Set, but his plan is opposed by Earth\'s heroes.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/233', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/233/atlantis_attacks?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(235, 'Blood and Thunder', 'jpg', 'Driven mad by the machinations of the evil Valkyrie, Thor sets out to destroy the Nine Worlds but is opposed by the Silver Surfer, Warlock and the Infinity Watch.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/235', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/235/blood_and_thunder?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(240, 'Days of Future Present', 'jpg', 'An adult Franklin Richards travels back from the year 2017 to repair perceived "inaccuracies" in the timeline by altering reality. Richards\' tampering of reality triggers a Sentinel program that awakens Ahab, the mutant hound-master, who attempts to apprehend the adult Richards in order to prevent any deviations from the timeline that spurs the Sentinel-ruled North America.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/240', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/240/days_of_future_present?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(29, 'Infinity War', 'jpg', 'The Magus, the purged, evil side of Adam Warlock believed to have been dead, has returned in order to collect the Infinity Gems and recreate the Infinity Gauntlet itself. He sent evil doppelgangers of Marvel\'s superheroes to attack and usurp the originals. Thanos, exiled since his defeat during the Infinity Gauntlet event, learned of the Magus\' plans and set out to aid Adam Warlock and the heroes in defending the universe.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/29', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/29/infinity_war?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(263, 'Mutant Massacre', 'jpg', 'The underground community of mutants known as the Morlocks are slaughtered by the villainous Marauders at the behest of Mister Sinister. Investigating, the X-Men, X-Factor and other heroes find themselves locked in a life or death struggle to save the surviving Morlocks from extermination.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/263', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/263/mutant_massacre?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(271, 'Secret Wars II', 'jpg', 'The omnipotent Beyonder comes to Earth to better understand the concept of desire as the heroes assemble to combat the threat he poses.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/271', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/271/secret_wars_ii?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(280, 'X-Tinction Agenda', 'jpg', 'Genoshan forces attack Xavier\'s School in an attempt to make the X-Men pay for their "crimes" against the island nation.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/280', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/280/x-tinction_agenda?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(318, 'Dark Reign', 'jpg', 'Norman Osborn came out the hero of Secret Invasion, and now the former Green Goblin has been handed control of the Marvel Universe. With his Cabal and the Dark Avengers at his side, can anything stop this long time villain from reshaping the world in his own image? And what has become of the heroes?', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/318', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/318/dark_reign?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(229, 'Annihilation', 'jpg', 'Parallel stories pitting the Silver Surfer, Nova, Ronan the Accuser and the Super-Skrull against Annihilus and his forces lead into a climatic six-issue war written by Keith Giffen with art by Andrea DiVito! Follow the machinations of Thanos, the power of Galactus and the early seeds that will create the Guardians of the Galaxy!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/229', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/229/annihilation?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(116, 'Acts of Vengeance!', 'jpg', 'Loki sets about convincing the super-villains of Earth to attack heroes other than those they normally fight in an attempt to destroy the Avengers to absolve his guilt over inadvertently creating the team in the first place.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/116', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/116/acts_of_vengeance?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(252, 'Inferno', 'jpg', 'The demon-sorcerer N\'astirh not only wished to rule Limbo, but Earth as well. He conceived of a plot to kidnap 13 human babies in order to sacrifice them in a ritual known as Inferno. Using the babies\' energy, he opened a portal between Limbo and Earth, which grew unnaturally hot and people began to succumb to their evil desires. Inferno had begun.', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/252', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/252/inferno?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(333, 'Monsters Unleashed', 'jpg', 'Watch out beginning in January 2017 as Monsters Unleashed rumbles into the Marvel Universe with terrifying threats new and old! Marvel\'s top heroes face monstrous challenges in a five-issue limited series written by Cullen Bunn and featuring the artistic talents of Adam Kubert, Greg Land, Salvador Larroca, Steve McNiven, and Leinil Yu! Can anybody stop the Monsters Unleashed? ', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/333', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/333/monsters_unleashed?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(337, 'Monsters Unleashed', 'jpg', 'Watch out as Monsters Unleashed rumbles into the Marvel Universe with terrifying threats new and old! Marvel\'s top heroes face monstrous challenges in a five-issue limited series written by Cullen Bunn and featuring the artistic talents of Adam Kubert, Greg Land, Salvador Larroca, Steve McNiven, and Leinil Yu! Can anybody stop the Monsters Unleashed? ', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/337', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/337/monsters_unleashed?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(336, 'Secret Empire', 'jpg', 'Steve Rogers has gone rogue and taken over the United States! It\'s up to the united forces of the Avengers, the Champions, the X-Men and more to bring down one of their own in the nine-issue limited series written by Nick Spencer!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/336', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/336/secret_empire?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(316, 'X-Men: Battle of the Atom', 'jpg', 'The presence of the original X-Men in the modern day has drawn mutants from the future back in time for a clash that will determine the fate of their race! With the timestream unraveling and civil war on the horizon, this 10-issue event features the talents of Brian Michael Bendis, Jason Aaron, Brian Wood, Frank Cho and many more!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/316', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/316/x-men_battle_of_the_atom?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(306, 'X-Men: Schism', 'jpg', 'A new Hellfire Club unleashes Sentinels on Utopia and causes a split in the X-Men! While Cyclops would mobilize the youth of mutantkind against those who would threaten them, Wolverine seeks to teach the next generation a new way. Writer Jason Aaron and an unparalleled team of artists explore this turning point in X-Men history with a five-issue event!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/306', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/306/x-men_schism?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2'),
	(319, 'Original Sin', 'jpg', 'Earth\'s Mightiest Heroes discover Uatu, the Watcher, dead on the moon, a murder mystery ensues that will reveal shocking secrets about every major Marvel character! Jason Aaron and Mike Deodato lead the Avengers, Spider-Man, the Hulk and many more on status-quo altering eight-past adventure!', 'http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/events/319', 'http://marvel.com/comics/events/319/original_sin?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2');
INSERT INTO `series` (`seriesId`, `seriesTitle`, `seriesExtension`, `seriesDescription`, `seriesDetail`, `seriesRating`, `seriesStart`, `seriesEnd`, `seriesComics`) VALUES
	(1945, 'Avengers: The Initiative (2007 - 2010)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/1945/avengers_the_initiative_2007_-_2010?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'T', '2007', '2010', 42),
	(2005, 'Deadpool (1997 - 2002)', 'jpg', 'Wade Wilson: Heartless Merc With a Mouth or...hero? Laugh, cry and applaud at full volume for the mind-bending adventures of Deadpool, exploring the psyche and crazed adventures of Marvel\'s most unstable personality!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/2005/deadpool_1997_-_2002?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1997', '2002', 71),
	(2045, 'Marvel Premiere (1972 - 1981)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/2045/marvel_premiere_1972_-_1981?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1972', '1981', 61),
	(17765, 'FREE COMIC BOOK DAY 2013 1 (2013)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/17765/free_comic_book_day_2013_1_2013?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2013', '2013', 0),
	(3374, 'Hulk (2008 - 2012)', 'jpg', 'General Thunderbolt Ross spent years hunting the Hulk, but now he\'s become one himself! As the rampaging Red Hulk, Ross strives to reconcile the man he used to be with the monster he\'s becomes, smashing anything that moves along the way!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/3374/hulk_2008_-_2012?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2008', '2012', 104),
	(13082, 'Ant-Man & the Wasp (2010 - 2011)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/13082/ant-man_the_wasp_2010_-_2011?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2010', '2011', 3),
	(1991, 'Avengers (1963 - 1996)', 'jpg', 'Avengers Assemble! Iron Man, Thor, Captain America and the rest of Earth\'s Mightiest Heroes unite to stand against the threats none can face alone! See the Avengers go up against Ultron, Kang, the Masters of Evil and more over three decades of epic action!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/1991/avengers_1963_-_1996?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1963', '1996', 403),
	(354, 'Avengers (1998 - 2004)', 'jpg', 'The Avengers return! Earth\'s Mightiest Heroes reunite with their biggest guns at the forefront to take on familiar enemies and new threats alike! Featuring the work of Kurt Busiek, George Perez and other quintessential Avengers creators!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/354/avengers_1998_-_2004?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'T+', '1998', '2004', 89),
	(23600, 'Avengers by Brian Michael Bendis: The Complete Collection Vol. 2 (2017)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/23600/avengers_by_brian_michael_bendis_the_complete_collection_vol_2_2017?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2017', '2017', 1),
	(1996, 'Captain America (1968 - 1996)', 'jpg', 'The Star-Spangled Avenger fights for freedom! Emerging from years on ice following World War II, Steve Rogers must adapt to a world that has gone on without him while also protecting his nation from the forces that would conspire to tear it apart!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/1996/captain_america_1968_-_1996?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1968', '1996', 355),
	(1997, 'Captain America (1998 - 2002)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/1997/captain_america_1998_-_2002?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1998', '2002', 50),
	(23810, 'Captain America by Mark Waid, Ron Garney & Andy Kubert (2017)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/23810/captain_america_by_mark_waid_ron_garney_andy_kubert_2017?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2017', '2017', 1),
	(3743, 'Defenders (1972 - 1986)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/3743/defenders_1972_-_1986?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1972', '1986', 152),
	(8842, 'Incredible Hulks (2010 - 2011)', 'jpg', 'Nobody loves you like your family--and nobody can you make you quite as crazy! With his son Skaar, cousin She-Hulk, ex-wife Red She-Hulk and more, Bruce Banner, aka the Incredible Hulk, attempts to harness his Gamma-powered brood for good!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/8842/incredible_hulks_2010_-_2011?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2010', '2011', 64),
	(16583, 'Indestructible Hulk (2012 - 2014)', 'jpg', 'Hulk - Indestructible force more weapon than man. Banner - smartest man alive. Combined they are the Strongest, Smartest Weapon on the planet! And NOW! the INDESTRUCTIBLE HULK is an Agent of S.H.I.E.L.D.!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/16583/indestructible_hulk_2012_-_2014?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2012', '2014', 42),
	(16593, 'Iron Man (2012 - 2014)', 'jpg', 'Tony Stark-Iron Man: Technological visionary, wealthy playboy, unparalleled engineer, and armored Avenger. His greatest invention becomes his greatest mistake. Iron Man must act fast...and Tony Stark must build faster! The lethal techno virus Extremis is out in the wild and out for grabs to the highest bidder! It\'s up to Tony Stark to contain it and that means creating a new suit of armor...NOW!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/16593/iron_man_2012_-_2014?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2012', '2014', 58),
	(2029, 'Iron Man (1968 - 1996)', 'jpg', 'The Armored Avenger battles super villains as well as corporate sabotage and his own personal demons in this landmark series! See the stories that formed the basis for Tony Stark becoming a household name!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/2029/iron_man_1968_-_1996?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1968', '1996', 337),
	(23915, 'Iron Man Epic Collection: Doom (2018)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/23915/iron_man_epic_collection_doom_2018?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2018', '2018', 1),
	(789, 'Dark Avengers (2012 - 2013)', 'jpg', 'Most of the Marvel Universe has given up on career super villains like Juggernaut, Moonstone and Crossbones, but criminal-turned-Avenger Luke Cage believes everybody deserves a second chance. Can the former Power Man turn this crew around?', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/789/dark_avengers_2012_-_2013?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'T', '2012', '2013', 16),
	(2085, 'Universe X (2000 - 2001)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/2085/universe_x_2000_-_2001?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2000', '2001', 14),
	(378, 'Earth X (1999 - 2000)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/378/earth_x_1999_-_2000?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1999', '2000', 14),
	(465, 'Hulk (1999 - 2008)', 'jpg', 'The Hulk goes from fugitive to interstellar gladiator in this eclectic series featuring Greg Pak\'s classic Planet Hulk epic!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/465/hulk_1999_-_2008?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1999', '2008', 119),
	(2021, 'Incredible Hulk (1962 - 1999)', 'jpg', 'Trapped in a the radioactive blast of a Gamma Bomb, withdrawn Doctor Bruce Banner becomes the rampaging Incredible Hulk! Witness the evolution of Marvel\'s most unstoppable force, from sinister brute to uncontrollable beast and every stage in between.', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/2021/incredible_hulk_1962_-_1999?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1962', '1999', 379),
	(2983, 'Incredible Hulk Annual (1976 - 1994)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/2983/incredible_hulk_annual_1976_-_1994?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1976', '1994', 16),
	(22424, 'Incredible Hulk Epic Collection: The Hulk Must Die (2017)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/22424/incredible_hulk_epic_collection_the_hulk_must_die_2017?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2017', '2017', 1),
	(2572, 'Iron Man (1998 - 2004)', 'jpg', 'The Golden Avenger rockets into the 21st century with new technology, new enemies, new loves and even his own armor turning against him!', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/2572/iron_man_1998_-_2004?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '1998', '2004', 90),
	(977, 'Irredeemable Ant-Man (2006 - 2007)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/977/irredeemable_ant-man_2006_-_2007?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', 'T', '2006', '2007', 12),
	(3722, 'Killraven (2002 - 2003)', 'jpg', '', 'http://marvel.com/comics/series/3722/killraven_2002_-_2003?utm_campaign=apiRef&utm_source=3e34603d82ff4d468843e222ddb951b2', '', '2002', '2003', 6),
